  "remarks": "He was sentenced to 15 years in prison in Indonesia in January 2022. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 8 Jun. 2010. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2253 (2015) was concluded on 7 Jun. 2018. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 15 November 2021.; Listing: Listed on: 16 May 2005 (amended on 17 Apr. 2019, 27 May 2022, 6 Oct 2025)",
